name: FitXR: The Original VR Fitness App
summary:
Fitness that doesn't feel like work. 

FitXR transforms exercise into play with immersive VR workouts that feel more like a rhythm game than the gym. Step into your headset and smash, dance, and move your way to real results — all from home.

Jump into Boxing, Dance, HIIT, Sculpt, Combat, and Zumba® classes designed to keep you motivated and having fun. Every workout is guided by certified coaches who bring energy, expertise, and encouragement to every session.

Here’s what makes FitXR different:
